## Running Tests

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"
pytest tests/ -v
```

With coverage:

```bash
pytest tests/ --cov=llm_os_shell --cov-report=term-missing
```

Test suite covers:
- Risk classification (50+ cases across all levels)
- LLM backend abstraction and fallback behavior
- Command execution (builtins, pipelines, redirects)
- Configuration loading and env overrides
- Shell confirmation flow
- Structured logging

